                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/china‚%2580%2599s-thirteenth-five-year-plan-paves-way-co2-emissions-peak">China‚Äôs Thirteenth Five-Year Plan Paves the Way for a CO2 Emissions Peak</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Xinjiang&#32;Windmills.jpg" alt="" title="" width="180" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
