                <div class="field-content"><h3><i>From the Paris Climate Negotiations</i></h3>

<p>COP-21 provided key insights into China‚Äôs evolving view on emissions MRV as national leaders committed to continue building monitoring systems and implementing verification protocols, including third-party verification, particularly for its seven regional pilot emissions trading schemes (ETS) and planned national program. In COP-21‚Äôs second week, the Chinese delegation hosted a <a href="http://www.chinatoday.com.cn/chinese/economy/ls/201512/t20151209_800044493.html">‚ÄúChina MRV System‚Äù side event</a> that brought together academics, government officials and policy experts to discuss China‚Äôs capacity to monitor and verify carbon emissions.</p></div>
