  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Shenzhen, a city of 11 million people just north of Hong Kong, has announced that it will begin emission trading on June 17.  Shenzhen is one of the <a href="../blog-posts/why-does-china-want-carbon-trading">seven Chinese cities and provinces that have been developing pilot programs for carbon emissions trading</a>.</p></div>
