  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>‚ÄúThe challenge for China is to find a third carbon pathway, one offering a high quality of life for its people, but at much lower emissions per capita than any of the developed country models,‚Äù said WRI China Country Director and Renmin University Professor <a href="http://www.wri.org/profile/zou-ji">Zou Ji</a> at WRI‚Äôs official side event at the UN Climate Conference in Tianjin last week.</p></div>
